infos.value: ...H-hey.
What do you lot think you're doing?
You should know this is Dynverk Cathedral you're barging into!
I am Lu'Cia, commander of Rundall's third division, «Calorum».
Rundall, you say!?
Unfortunately, Lord Sadali isn't here at the moment. You'll have to come back another time.
My, how fortunate.
W-watch it!
If you intend to mock us...
How about it, King Jayden?
Jayden?
King Jayden of Rundall couldn't possibly be here, too...?
I caught word that Sadali was mining illegally all over the continent, collecting Crystals.
I have come today to seize them.
You must be joking!
Do you really think we'll simply hand over our precious Crystals?
I suppose not. Then we'll just take them by force.
W-we won't allow it!
You should be honored.
You two are now part of the next chapter of my great story.
To be continued...
